PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Public Works and Government Services of DINO CHIESA, of North York, Ontario, as a director of the Board of Directors of Canada Mortgage and Housing Corporation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Cuckoo Kochar, whose term has expired.
